nh Tiêu - 贈陳名標</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-Ng%C5%A9-Ph%C3%BAc/author-nDDIeBcr0ae9JEbukHfORA">Hoàng Ngũ Phúc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-Vi-th%E1%BA%ADp-l%E1%BB%A5c-b%C3%ACnh-s%E1%BB%B1-sung-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-C%E1%BB%91c-qu%E1%BA%ADn-ph%C3%B2ng-ng%E1%BB%B1-ph%C3%A1n-quan/poem-MFF_HoVQ7OCaWWzHCcGVEw">Tống Vi thập lục bình sự sung Đồng Cốc quận phòng ngự phán quan - 送韋十六評事充同谷郡防禦判官</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/V%C3%A3n-thu-tham-thi%E1%BB%81n/poem-8yN40zXtbKGw_HZ44xR_oQ">Vãn thu tham thiền - 晚秋參禪</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-K%E1%BB%B3/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-III/poem-eSfXfOv63GTAmlxrXY7l-g">Vô đề (III) - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-K%E1%BB%B3/author-1swHDuDfqhjQRVvirtpDBQ">Phạm Kỳ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
